{
  "name": "@huo15/openclaw-enhance",
  "version": "5.3.2",
  "description": "火一五·克劳德·龙虾增强插件 v5.3.2 — 对标 Claude Code Agent Harness，非侵入式增强 OpenClaw：移除插件运行期外部进程调用（企业扫描器友好）；记忆整合（corpus supplement + Why/How-to-apply 两段式）、工具安全补充、statusline 观测（模型/思考档/通道/会话）、spawn_task 一键 CLI 派发、ExitPlanMode 审批闭环、skill-installer 工具、工作流、任务/章节/触发器追踪、仪表盘、输出自检、模式闸门、定时任务桥接",
  "type": "module",
  "main": "index.ts",
  "openclaw": {
    "extensions": [
      "./index.ts"
    ],
    "build": {
      "openclawVersion": "2026.4.11"
    },
    "compat": {
      "pluginApi": ">=2026.4.11"
    }
  },
  "bin": {
    "openclaw-enhance-setup": "./scripts/setup.sh"
  },
  "keywords": [
    "openclaw",
    "plugin",
    "enhance",
    "memory",
    "safety",
    "agent"
  ],
  "author": "jobzhao15",
  "license": "MIT",
  "peerDependencies": {
    "openclaw": ">=2026.4.11"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "@sinclair/typebox": "^0.34.49",
    "better-sqlite3": "^11.0.0"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@types/better-sqlite3": "^7.6.0",
    "typescript": "^5.5.0"
  },
  "files": [
    "index.ts",
    "openclaw.plugin.json",
    "src/**/*",
    "templates/**/*",
    "scripts/**/*"
  ],
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "https://cnb.cool/huo15/ai/huo15-openclaw-enhance"
  }
}
